#title "FM Operator Commands Test"
#description "Tests FM operator commands: AR, DR, SR, RR, SL, TL"

$Part1=YM2612@1
$Part2=YM2151

* Part1 YM2612 FM Test
@Part1
@AR10 @DR20 @SR5 @RR8 @SL6 @TL42
@AL1 @FB3
t120 l8
o5 c2 d2 e2 f2 | g2 a2 b2 >c2

* Part2 OPM Test (YM2151)
@Part2
@AR12 @DR18 @SR4 @RR6 @SL8 @TL40
@AL2 @FB2
t120 l8 
o4 c2 d2 e2 f2 | g2 a2 b2 >c2
